# React Native + Expo Rules

## Coding Standards

- Use TypeScript with strict mode
- Prefer functional components with hooks
- Use React.FC for typed props
- Always type useState and useEffect

## Expo Patterns

- Use `npx expo install` for modules
- Prefer Expo SDK over third-party native libs
- Use `Platform.select()` for platform differences

